This will output:

* The values of moments Î¼â‚‚â€², Î¼â‚„â€², Î¼â‚†â€²
* A table of possible (a\*, b\*) values and corresponding `n1`, `n2` allocations
* Conditions satisfied for each case
* A graph showing which points satisfy conditions (i), (ii), and (iii)

